reviewText: We watched this growing up and it helped us learn abcs and numbers. Was super excited to find it 23 years later for my kids!
Are these program made on dvd yet? There were great for my child, now I want them on DVD for my grandchildren
This VHS played a huge part in my upbringing.  I learned my letters and numbers with Simon and Chloe on the farm and I cannot wait to share this with my children.
